    public class NativeModule
extends Object
implements com.google.devtools.build.lib.syntax.ClassObject, com.google.devtools.build.lib.skylarkinterface.SkylarkValue
    Represents a native variable available in Skylark extension files. It's responsible for handling calls like native.java_library(...) in .bzl files.
